name: LOWO ROBO
description:
LOWO ROBO

LOWO ROBO is the first flying animal robot experimental by OBYØR Laboratory. Born on 2035.

Comes with rolling laser eyes and ultrasound technology. The Ultrasound waves emitted by LOWO ROBO bounce off objects in their environment. Enemy blood is his favorite food.

LOWO ROBO is small
LOWO ROBO is flying
LOWO ROBO is black
LOWO ROBO is scary

LOWO ROBO IS A GLITCH!
